ntry.</p><p>This prize is non-transferable and cannot be exchanged for monetary value; no cash alternatives to the stated prize will be offered. Any exchanges are at the retailer's discretion.</p><p>If you are the winner of the Prize the receipt by you of the Prize is conditional upon you complying with any and all applicable laws, rules and regulations including, without limitation these terms and conditions.</p><p>By entering the Competition (i) you agree that your name and likeness may be used by Voxblock for advertising and publicity purposes, and (ii) you agree to participate in such promotional activity may require, in each case without additional remuneration.</p><p>(If) entering your email address, you are agreeing to be added to our emailing list, and will receive emails from hello@voxblock.co.uk.</p><p>You may unsubscribe from emails from <a href=\"mailto:hello@voxblock.co.uk\">hello@voxblock.co.uk</a> at any time.</p><p>Voxblock reserves the right to (i) cancel this promotion, (ii) cancel or refuse any individual’s entry and (iii) amend these terms and conditions (and will use reasonable endeavours to notify changes to entrants and potential entrants.</p><p>Subject to the maximum extent permitted by law, Voxblock and their associated companies and agents exclude responsibility and all liabilities arising from (i) any postponement or cancellation of the Competition, (ii) any loss or, changes to, postponement of or use of the Prize, and (iii) any act or default of any third party supplier, which are beyond both brands reasonable control.</p><p> </p>",
